OL,5, Former Wimbledon champion Boris Becker 
OL,6, has been jailed for two and a half     
OL,7, years for hiding #2.5m worth of assets 
OL,8, and loans to avoid paying debts.       
OL,10,FThe 54-year-old six-time Grand Slam    
OL,11,Fchampion was found guilty of four      
OL,12,Fcharges under the Insolvency Act.      
OL,14,FThe case centred on Becker's bankruptcy
OL,15,Fin June 2017 resulting from an unpaid  
OL,16,Floan of more than #3m on his luxury    
OL,17,Festate in Mallorca, Spain.             
OL,19,FJudge Deborah Taylor said he had shown 
OL,20,Fno remorse or acceptance of guilt.     
